## 5. Entity Layer (Database Tables)

Entities map Java classes to MySQL tables using JPA annotations.

### `Product.java`

```java
@Entity
@Table(name = "products")
@Data @NoArgsConstructor @AllArgsConstructor
public class Product {
    @Id
    @GeneratedValue(strategy = GenerationType.IDENTITY)
    private Long id;              // Auto-increment primary key

    @Column(nullable = false)
    private String name;          // Product name (required)

    private String description;   // Optional description
    private String manufacturer;  // Optional manufacturer
    private Integer quantity;     // Stock quantity
    private Double price;         // Unit price
}
```

**Generated MySQL Table:**
```sql
CREATE TABLE products (
    id BIGINT AUTO_INCREMENT PRIMARY KEY,
    name VARCHAR(255) NOT NULL,
    description VARCHAR(255),
    manufacturer VARCHAR(255),
    quantity INT,
    price DOUBLE
);
```

