## 8. Security Layer (JWT Authentication)

### How JWT Authentication Works (Step by Step)

```
┌──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┐
│                    REQUEST LIFECYCLE                                      │
├──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┤
│                                                                          │
│  HTTP Request arrives at port 8088                                       │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ▼                                                                  │
│  [CORS Filter] — Checks if origin is allowed (localhost:3000/5173)       │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ▼                                                                  │
│  [JwtAuthenticationFilter] — Extracts & validates JWT from header        │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ├── Token valid → Sets Authentication in SecurityContext           │
│       │                                                                  │
│       └── No token / Invalid → SecurityContext remains empty             │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ▼                                                                  │
│  [SecurityFilterChain] — Checks authorization rules                      │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ├── Public endpoint (/api/auth/login, /signup) → Allow through     │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ├── Authenticated user → Allow through to controller               │
│       │                                                                  │
│       └── No authentication → Return 401 Unauthorized                    │
│       │                                                                  │
│       ▼                                                                  │
│  [Controller] — Processes request, returns response                      │
│                                                                          │
└──────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────┘
```

